high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the potato out of the fridge, then close the door.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink and turn on the faucet, after a couple seconds turn the faucet off and remove the now clean potato.
Turn left and walk over to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave to the right of the apple and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Go right and then turn right and turn to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick up the potato from inside and shut the door.
Go left and then left again and turn right to face the sink.
Put the potato in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the potato up again.
Go left and walk to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the counter across from you, then turn right and go to the refrigerator on the other side of the kitchen.
Take out the potato on the left side of the bottom shelf, in the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the sink on your right.
Place the potato in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the potato off, turn the water off, and remove the potato from the sink.
Turn to your left and go to the microwave on the counter across from you.
Place the potato in the microwave, on the kitchen counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean and cold potato in the microwave.
